enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve consuming characters from the queue up to a specified sequence, with case insensitivity.
The matches method is used within consumeToIgnoreCase, which is directly related to the functionality of chompToIgnoreCase.
matchChomp is invoked after consumeToIgnoreCase within chompToIgnoreCase, ensuring the sequence is matched and removed from the queue.
consumeTo is functionally similar to consumeToIgnoreCase but case-sensitive, providing a basis for understanding the case-insensitive version.
